	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"A few things, but not of much interest.
	$LF
]div
[h4 id=HasHeDoneAnyTimeattacksOnThisSite 
	" Has he done any timeattacks on this site?
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"He once did a speedrun of 
	(__wikiLink|displaytext=Sonic the Hedgehog 2|href=/658S)
	" which somehow managed to earn a star, though it was quickly obsoleted using a variety of obvious shortcuts which he somehow didn't notice. Given the extreme level of perfection that has come to be expected here, he is unlikely to ever try speedrunning again.
	$LF
]div
[h4 id=SoWhatElseDoesHeDoHere 
	" So, what else does he do here?
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"Not particularly much. He occasionally posts on the forums, but usually doesn't have the time. He rarely even manages to update this page, leaving it outdated for years on end.
	$LF
]div
